  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3770107">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3770107/" class="title-link">口号作用</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3770107"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/46244907/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u46244907-30.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/46244907/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">散游</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-09-30"
      class="main-meta">2010-09-30 14:52:58</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3770107_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                       于当今众多回忆录一样，我带着较为独特的眼光去读这本《郭汝瑰回忆录》，感觉比较精彩的是抗日战争那段，也许是从另一个侧面去理解当时的战争，写的很细，包括有很多数字统计。     当看到解放战争这段，正好单位组织观看《建国大业》的电影，由此对比觉得，当一个政权彻...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3770107/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 4没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3770107_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3770107_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










